Summary: moving star like object spotted over Harrisburg...AGAIN
divs: Sighting DetailsThis time it was only a single moving star like object, last night there were two in unison, I reported this event last night but accidently reported it as happening in August, correction...it happened last night. But tonight, just a while ago, my boyfriend and I were outside getting on our motorcycle when we spotted just a single moving star like object just to the north of us headed northeast. It was a dimmer light this time, kind of bluish, no flashes, no sound. Last nights incident gave me a feeling of elation, tonights incident however leaves me feeling moody and unsure. I wonder if this has any relevence. Thanks for letting me share.
